text: Filip Bergmark (born April 29, 1995) is a Swedish ice hockey defenceman. He is currently playing with Örebro HK of the Swedish Hockey League (SHL). Bergmark made his Swedish Hockey League debut playing with Örebro HK during the 2014–15 SHL season.http://www.svenskafans.com/hockeyzon/orebro-i-praktiken-klara-for- historiskt-slutspel-527007.aspx ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Örebro HK players Category:Swedish ice hockey defencemen
